---
import '../styles/about.css';
---

<section class="about-section" id="about">
  <h3 class="section-title"><span class="section-prompt">></span> About</h3>
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-pull reveal" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 32px;">
      <span>For over 10 years, I've built systems where failure isn't an option: mission-critical legal-tech infrastructure serving 100,000+ lawyers filing directly to Italian courts.</span>
      <span>I find what actually needs solving, not just what I'm told to build. My job isn't just writing code. It's protecting your business from the technical mistakes that cost you most.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-body reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.12s;">
      <p>Before we write a line of code, you'll have a clear picture of what's realistic, where the risks are, and what it will take to get it right. <strong>That's not a promise, it's how I've worked for 10 years.</strong></p>
      <p>Falling behind doesn't happen all at once. It happens <strong>one small wrong decision at a time</strong>: a system that breaks under load, a rebuild you didn't budget for. And while you're putting out those fires, your competitors are already automating, cutting costs, adopting AI. They're not waiting.</p>
      <p><strong>If your tech is keeping you up at night, or if you know it soon will, I'm the call you make before it gets expensive.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <a href="#" class="cta-btn">&gt; RUN_CONSULTATION</a>
  </div>
</section>
